Here’s an example for the Python 3.10.0 release:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://discussions.xojoc.pw/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.python.org%2Fdownloads%2Frelease%2Fpython-3100%2F" rel="ugc"&gt;https://discussions.xojoc.pw/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.python.org%2Fdownloads%2Frelease%2Fpython-3100%2F&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;or for the “QBE compiler”:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://discussions.xojoc.pw/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fc9x.me%2Fcompile%2F" rel="ugc"&gt;https://discussions.xojoc.pw/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fc9x.me%2Fcompile%2F&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It also has a companion bookmarklet that redirects to discussions.xojoc.pw for the current page.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It’s written in Python: &lt;a href="https://github.com/xojoc/discussions" rel="ugc"&gt;https://github.com/xojoc/discussions&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Any feedback is welcome :)&lt;/p&gt;

